<i>Hyung—</i>

13
00:02:09,740 --> 00:02:10,920
<i>Hyung.</i>

14
00:02:10,920 --> 00:02:12,350
<i>Hyung!</i>

15
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:29,300
Yoon Soo Wan...

16
00:02:30,350 --> 00:02:32,400
How do you know him?

17
00:02:34,780 --> 00:02:36,620
He's my brother.

18
00:02:39,750 --> 00:02:41,700
And my brother...

19
00:02:42,460 --> 00:02:44,730
died ten years ago.

20
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:54,760
<i>[10 years ago, Seoul]</i>

21
00:03:23,190 --> 00:03:28,060
My brother died ten years ago on that night.

22
00:03:42,870 --> 00:03:48,780
<i>What was I holding on to all this time?</i>

23
