<i>[October 2020 Fall/Winter Color Map]</i>

27
00:04:00,570 --> 00:04:02,640
<i>What was I trying to forget</i>

28
00:04:03,170 --> 00:04:07,490
<i>that I've lived this tirelessly?</i>

29
00:04:12,290 --> 00:04:17,530
<i>What was I hating and resenting</i>

30
00:04:21,810 --> 00:04:24,390
<i>that I have become</i>

31
00:04:26,190 --> 00:04:28,350
<i>this emotionless?</i>

32
